  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The proposed indication for the investigational heat-treated varicella-zoster virus (VZV)
      vaccine is the prevention of herpes zoster (HZ) and HZ-related complications in
      immunocompromised individuals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
